title: Pictured Rocks National Lakeshore: Post Office
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Goods & Services     Post Office                Post Office         Munising Post Office NPS photo by Ed Lasich  Pictured Rocks National Lakeshore is located on the south shore of Lake Superior between the communities of Munising and Grand Marais.  There are several post offices in the area.
